title: Dragoncon EFForums Audio 2013 MP
description:
Audio from the 2013 EFForums track at Dragon*Con.

30+ Hours of audio covering everything from the NSA revelations, and Geotagging and GPS games, through cryptography and P2P lawsuits to 'how to write erotic ficton and 10 rules for dealing with police encounters

Also includes the annual favourite, Hacking 101

More details, including a full program list is at http://eff.dragoncon.org/2013-schedule/
